    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>When you join the College of Whispers at 3rd level, you gain the ability to make your weapon attacks magically toxic to a creature's mind.</p><p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend one use of your Bardic Inspiration to deal an extra [[/damage 2d6 type=psychic]] damage to that target. You can do so only once per round on your turn.</p><p>The psychic damage increases when you reach certain levels in this class, increasing to [[/damage 3d6]] at 5th level, [[/damage 5d6]] at 10th level, and [[/damage 8d6]] at 15th level.</p></div>",
